                            <comment id="13213558" author="lehmi" created="Wed, 22 Feb 2012 12:14:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you provide us with a sample pdf, please?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13213585" author="dave.smith" created="Wed, 22 Feb 2012 12:55:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can not due to privacy reasons, but here is all the info you need&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4 0 obj&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;&amp;lt;/Type/XObject&lt;br/&gt;
/Subtype/Image&lt;br/&gt;
/Width 2552&lt;br/&gt;
/Height 3300&lt;br/&gt;
/BitsPerComponent 1&lt;br/&gt;
/ColorSpace/DeviceGray&lt;br/&gt;
/Filter /CCITTFaxDecode&lt;br/&gt;
/DecodeParms &amp;lt;&amp;lt;/Columns 2552 /Rows 3300&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/Length 82636&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
stream&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;First 10 bytes     0,18,-64,29,5,50,96,2,80,3,-96&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first line is  white 43 bits, black 2432 and then white 51 then EOL ... When you decode the 2432 line your extended line length is wrong because when you built the table you started at 0 not 1792&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13227048" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 11 Mar 2012 13:58:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was able to double check the patch using a sample pdf Dave sent me in private as it is confidential.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I added the patch in revision 1299358 as proposed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the contribution!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
